McCat IS LITERALLY A MEME COIN. NO UTILITY. NO PROMISES. NO EXPECTATION OF FINANCIAL RETURN. JUST 100% MEMES.!! 😺

I ACTUALLY WANTED TO WRITE MORE ABOUT McCat TO MAKE IT LOOKS GOOD,BUT I WAS LAZY.

I’D  RATHER EAT POPCORN WHILE LOOKING AT THE CHART TO MAKE SURE IT STAYS GREEN THAN WRITE AT LENGTH.

HOW TO BUY

Create a Wallet

download metamask or your wallet of choice from the app store or google play store for free. Desktop users, download the google chrome extension by going to metamask.io.

Get Some ETH

have ETH in your wallet to switch to $McCat. If you don’t have any ETH, you can buy directly on metamask, transfer from another wallet, or buy on another exchange and send it to your wallet.

Go to Uniswap

connect to Uniswap. Go to app.uniswap.org in google chrome or on the browser inside your Metamask app. Connect your wallet. Paste the $McCat token address into Uniswap, select McCat, and confirm. When Metamask prompts you for a wallet signature, sign.

Switch ETH for $McCat

Switch ETH for $McCat.
We have 2% taxes.
(you may need to use slippage 2%-5% during times of market volatility.)
